{"title":"ssh keygen","uid":"8a8cf02982a981a3981c312011f99772","slug":"ssh-keygen","date":"2025-01-07T09:06:00.000Z","updated":"2025-01-07T09:06:00.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ssh-keygen.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img.kidwen.top/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAMKZ8Uk3Z0SXl4caws_sVUAATJxcK-wAAIxwTEb6dopVs78RNHffPBfAQADAgADeAADNgQ.png","content":"<p>一般来说，一个github账号和一个gitlab账号，需要生成两个公钥和私钥，分别用于github和gitlab。下面介绍如何生成公钥和私钥。并且配置config文件，方便使用。</p>\n<h2 id=\"使用git-bash进入-ssh目录\"><a href=\"#使用git-bash进入-ssh目录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用git bash进入.ssh目录\"></a>使用git bash进入.ssh目录</h2><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-darker\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">cd</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">~/.ssh</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"生成公钥和私钥\"><a href=\"#生成公钥和私钥\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"生成公钥和私钥\"></a>生成公钥和私钥</h2><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-darker\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">ssh-keygen</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-t</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">ed25519</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-C</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">&lt;comment&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># 例如</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">ssh-keygen</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-t</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">ed25519</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-C</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">github@kidwen.top</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># 第一步输入文件名 例如 github_id_ed25519</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># 第二步输入密码 可以不用管</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># 第三步输入确认密码 可以不用管</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"将公钥添加到github\"><a href=\"#将公钥添加到github\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"将公钥添加到github\"></a>将公钥添加到github</h2><ol>\n<li>复制 github_id_ed25519.pub 文件内容</li>\n<li>打开github 点击头像 -&gt; settings -&gt; SSH and GPG keys -&gt; New SSH key</li>\n<li>将复制的内容粘贴到 key 中</li>\n<li>点击 Add SSH key</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"同样步骤可以再次生成一个其他名字的公钥和私钥\"><a href=\"#同样步骤可以再次生成一个其他名字的公钥和私钥\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"同样步骤可以再次生成一个其他名字的公钥和私钥\"></a>同样步骤可以再次生成一个其他名字的公钥和私钥</h2><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-darker\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">ssh-keygen</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-t</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">ed25519</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-C</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">gitlab@kidwen.top</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># 第一步输入文件名 例如 gitlab_id_ed25519</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># 第二步输入密码 可以不用管</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># 第三步输入确认密码 可以不用管</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"将公钥添加到gitlab\"><a href=\"#将公钥添加到gitlab\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"将公钥添加到gitlab\"></a>将公钥添加到gitlab</h2><ol>\n<li>复制 gitlab_id_ed25519.pub 文件内容</li>\n<li>打开gitlab 点击头像 -&gt; settings -&gt; SSH keys -&gt; Add SSH key</li>\n<li>将复制的内容粘贴到 key 中</li>\n<li>点击 Add key</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"配置-config-文件\"><a href=\"#配置-config-文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置 config 文件\"></a>配置 config 文件</h2><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-darker\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># 在.ssh目录下创建config文件</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">touch</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">config</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># 编辑config文件</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">vi</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">config</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># 在文件中添加以下内容</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">Host</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">github.com</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">HostName</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">github.com</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">PreferredAuthentications</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">publickey</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">IdentityFile</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">~/.ssh/github_id_ed25519</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">Host</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">gitlab.com</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">HostName</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">gitlab.com</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">PreferredAuthentications</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">publickey</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">IdentityFile</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">~/.ssh/gitlab_id_ed25519</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"测试是否成功\"><a href=\"#测试是否成功\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试是否成功\"></a>测试是否成功</h2><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-darker\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">ssh</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-T</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">github.com</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">ssh</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-T</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">gitlab.com</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"配置全局用户名和邮箱\"><a href=\"#配置全局用户名和邮箱\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置全局用户名和邮箱\"></a>配置全局用户名和邮箱</h2><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-darker\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">git</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">config</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">--global</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">user.name</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">kidwen</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">git</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">config</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">--global</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">user.email</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">kidwen@qq.com</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&quot;</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"配置当前仓库提交的用户名\"><a href=\"#配置当前仓库提交的用户名\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置当前仓库提交的用户名\"></a>配置当前仓库提交的用户名</h2><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-darker\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># 进入仓库目录  </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">cd</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">/path/to/your/repo</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># 配置用户名</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">git</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">config</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">--local</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E